&lt;p&gt;As a Sales Development Manager at Anthropic, you&#39;ll lead and scale our business development function to drive pipeline generation for our frontier AI products. You&#39;ll build and manage a high-performing team of BDRs, optimize our lead management processes, and collaborate closely with sales leadership to ensure alignment between pipeline generation and revenue goals. This is a critical role in scaling Anthropic&#39;s go-to-market engine during a period of hyper-growth.&lt;/p&gt;
