&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, lead, and scale a team of 8-12 BDRs focused on both inbound lead management and strategic outbound prospecting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with sales leadership to align pipeline generation with revenue targets across Startup and Enterprise segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and track KPIs for lead quality, conversion rates, and pipeline contribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create comprehensive training programs and career development paths for BDRs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with marketing to optimize lead quality and campaign effectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive adoption of sales tools and technologies (Salesforce, HubSpot, SQL) to improve team efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Pipeline Reviews with sales leadership - covering top of funnel health, conversion metrics, outbound progress, and marketing support / follow-through&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage relationships with cross-functional stakeholders including sales, marketing, and operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build scalable processes to support Anthropic&#39;s rapid growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and mentor BDRs on prospecting strategies, qualification techniques, and career development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
